Class Date

  • java.lang.Object
    • Project3.src.Date
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Date>
    public class Date
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Date>
    The Date class allows us to look at a formatted date and determine if the date are valid or not. year: the year of the date. month: the month of the date. day: numerical day of the date.
